CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 10, 1962, pg. 24, reads: "Seeking Title - This is expected to be the starting lineup for the cagers of Allegheny High School Friday night in their tilt against Fifth Avenue for the city championship. Members of the team, coached by Karl Fehrenbach, center, are left to right, Cephus Moore, James Biggart, Eddie Hardwick, Mike McGahev and Guy Proctor. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Allegheny High School basketball team players from left, Cephus Moore, James Biggart, Eddie Hardwick, Mike McGahev, and Guy Proctor, with coach Karl Fehrenbach in foreground, posed in gymnasium
